Package: binompoiscont
Title: Continuous versions of dbinom and dpois
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
     person("Crist-Jan", "Doedens", , "cfjdoedens@chance-matters.nl", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: The functions stat::dbinom(k, n, p) and stat::dpois(lambda, x) are restricted in that k, n, and lambda should be whole non negative integers. We introduce here the functional counterparts dbinom_continuous(k, n, p) and dpois(lambda, x) that have these restrictios lifted.
